decks.notes: This deck focuses on playing aggressively with Aragorn, King of Gondor as the commander. It includes a mix of control spells like Force of Will and Counterspell to disrupt opponents while also packing a punch with cards like True-Name Nemesis and Lightning Bolt. The deck aims to establish early board presence and maintain pressure on the opponent while controlling the game with counterspells and removal. It also includes efficient creatures like Brazen Borrower and Skyclave Apparition to deal with threats on the board. Overall, the key strategy is to overwhelm opponents with a combination of aggressive creatures, disruptive spells, and efficient removal to secure victory in the 1 vs 1 format of Duel Commander.

The deck focuses on using Arwen, Mortal Queen as the commander to lead an aggressive playstyle. It includes a variety of mana dorks and ramp spells to quickly build up resources and bring Arwen onto the battlefield early on. The deck also features a mix of disruptive creatures like Drannith Magistrate and Sanctifier en-Vec to control the opponent's plays. Additionally, the deck includes powerful combat-oriented cards like Questing Beast and Tarmogoyf to pressure the opponent and quickly close out the game. With a strong mix of ramp, disruption, and aggressive threats, the deck aims to overwhelm the opponent and secure a fast victory in a 1 vs 1 Duel Commander format.
